Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.59,0:00:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.48,0:00:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 這裏不是島嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.55,0:00:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼連上了陸地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毋須在意細節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.09,0:00:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃人才是關鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花劄也玩膩了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有別的餘興節目了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:03:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來狩獵大名之前必須要打倒你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面有點吵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.73,0:03:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒法冷靜思考了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溶遁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.65,0:03:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得手的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八尾和九尾的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於出現了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.23,0:04:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得通知他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.21,0:04:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八尾和九尾好像出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八尾和九尾出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大名們怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:41.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要抓他們來做談判的籌碼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 已經不需要大名們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.40,0:04:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說抓了那些傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會迫使各國給忍者聯軍施壓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但其實也只是為了逼出八尾和九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:05:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然八尾和九尾出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.16,0:05:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就沒必要兜圈子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那個雷影一開始就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些大名在這場戰爭中毫無交涉的價值可言
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要月之眼計畫成功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切就都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.40,0:05:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得黑絕和水影幹上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼說他們也是受雇於大名 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會坐視不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.04,0:05:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓黑絕繼續打持久戰
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.17,0:05:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把水影一行牽制在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能分散敵人的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那阿飛…你準備怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於要參戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.11,0:05:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先奪取替代品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四紫炎陣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個結界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算被穢土轉生操縱也一事無成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙就是最後一個了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要掛了 誰來救救我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.04,0:06:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查克拉用過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.69,0:06:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再用這個忍具了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會 明明很好用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝了 木葉的大塊頭
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.46,0:07:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才剛剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的判斷能力太差了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現階段的戰鬥 我們已經贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.65,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死守海岸線成功
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.08,0:07:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的登陸作戰失敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通靈之術
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.01,0:07:50.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.37,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:22.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比丁次還大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.61,0:08:27.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種不好的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是體型大的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的判斷力也不過如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過來 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:45.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,角都和日差先生那邊就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.81,0:08:47.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印班
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.32,0:08:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 外道魔像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.82,0:09:12.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是現在 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被擋下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.33,0:09:35.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.98,0:09:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懶所轄第一部隊的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.90,0:09:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了驚人的查克拉體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是何方神聖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.61,0:10:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接上第一部隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是個人形的大怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 操縱那傢伙的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.20,0:10:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是宇智波斑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須要重新制訂作戰計畫了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭目竟然行動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,判斷依據不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.03,0:10:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥之前那個模式 別用太過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.27,0:10:37.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵時刻力量用完 又該如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.53,0:10:40.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間管這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.44,0:10:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告 殺人蜂和漩渦鳴人兩人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經逃出結界 來到外界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.35,0:10:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個結界不是連人柱力都無法打破嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.43,0:10:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是兩個人柱力聯手破壞了結界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人意料之外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來蜂大人幫忙了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:06.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何打算
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去阻止人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綱手 你也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總部誰來指揮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.32,0:11:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木葉的鹿角
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.29,0:11:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.24,0:11:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.07,0:11:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 跟我來吧 綱手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷影大人 麻煩您別破壞牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.74,0:12:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全體退至海岸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土遁.山土之術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.70,0:12:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.52,0:12:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在強得離譜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.22,0:12:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在聯軍會議時
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.21,0:12:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從砂隱手鞠曾收集的情報來推測…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很可能是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據砂隱的風影給出的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人柱力的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.07,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像被封印在一個儀式用的巨大人形雕像裏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜂的章魚腳分身恐怕也被吸進去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.20,0:13:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…就是那個玩意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的絕招輕鬆就被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.65,0:13:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那玩意封印了人柱力的力量 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.44,0:13:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.28,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.78,0:13:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個忍具不會交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.75,0:13:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要忍具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只要裏面的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.57,0:13:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後會把忍具還給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們想要的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.97,0:14:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先利用持有九尾查克拉的金角銀角
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.25,0:14:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前線衝鋒陷陣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.10,0:14:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機成熟後再把金角銀角的九尾查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印進大個子的體內
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:16.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聯軍裏也有些能人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙作為敵人真是可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 那個大個子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹿丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.24,0:14:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧 鹿丸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.86,0:14:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧你了 丁次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又麻煩你了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連忍具一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丁座 快封印
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點把我封印起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.23,0:16:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怕 包圍他們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰局瞬間變得不利了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.04,0:16:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊和總部聯繫 重整旗鼓 懶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:50.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚就要降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.23,0:16:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好被夜襲對峙的準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這場戰爭不容有失 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要謹慎行事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多年的願望 月之眼計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.38,0:17:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日便可達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.34,0:17:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 已經得到了金角銀角
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八尾的查克拉只封印了少許
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.71,0:17:27.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一條章魚腿的量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.92,0:17:30.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒覺得有些操之過急
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上就按你的計畫行事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的棋子暫且保存起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 佐井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.95,0:18:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.08,0:18:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡卡西先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 能站崗的人到我身邊來集合
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不到敵人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:27.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.16,0:18:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退還是進攻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.18,0:18:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個部隊目前沒有隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.85,0:18:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加強此地的防守
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在命令到達之前待機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好 感知型的都集中在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,防守是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.70,0:18:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.76,0:18:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂子沒有任何感應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.33,0:18:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來他們應該是撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.74,0:18:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是穢土轉生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.70,0:19:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那利用不死之身持續戰鬥才是上策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.38,0:19:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道有更好的戰術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛羅大人 請用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.39,0:19:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須保存體力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不急 先給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.63,0:19:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給這位小小的老爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.79,0:19:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是土影
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人可能會趁夜突襲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 別放鬆警惕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的忍具在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還給我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.15,0:19:47.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都讓你別再用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.11,0:19:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:52.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明很好用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:54.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太浪費了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:20:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斑奪走忍具的事已經報告總部了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.80,0:20:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴他們尾獸查克拉被奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.56,0:20:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我失態了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.34,0:20:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果早點發現的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你們做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能阻止也是無可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 今天也算擊退敵人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.52,0:20:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八萬忍者聯軍 今天折損了四萬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.27,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十萬曉的部隊 今天折損了五萬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.96,0:20:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雙方都傷亡過半
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:50.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我方都是鮮活的生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.51,0:20:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方則…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就…來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.60,0:22:50.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,在你身邊的佐助 一直被仇恨所困
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.93,0:22:51.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,那天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.40,0:22:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,從那天起 你應該就察覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.88,0:22:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,下集火影忍者疾風傳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.65,0:22:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0005,,和解之印
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳴人感受到了父母的家庭之愛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.73,0:23:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍者之路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.83,0:23:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火影忍者劇場版
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全國火熱上映中
